<strong><span style="color: #FF0040">THE REALITY OF MAWLANA ASHRAF ALI THANWI BASED ON HIS AMAL QURANI<br /><br />READINGS IN AMAL QURANI<br /><br />PART 11<br /></span></strong><br />Another remedy for menstruation. Some Sahirs in order to seek and use the help of the shayatin write the ayat of the Quran with menstruation blood.<br /><br />He writes<br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal"><span style="color: #FF0000">In order to maintain menstruation write the following tawiz and tie it to your wrist and the (woman) should donate 5 coins in charity on behalf of the who ties the tawiz (ie the one who writes the tawiz)<br /><br />The tawiz is<br /><br />Oh Allah via the sake of Shaikh Muhammad Sadiq the major awliya son of Shaikh Ahmad Sirhindi Mujadid Alf Thani may Allah be please with him may the harm be removed and Allah is the curer and sufficient<br />(Amal Qurani pp.35-36 of Mawlana Ashraf Ali Thanwi and endorsed by Mufti Muhammad's Shafi, Mawlana Taqi Usmanis Father)</span></span></strong><br /></div></blockquote><br /><br /><div class="inline-attachment"><dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><img src="https://forum.salafiri.com/download/file.php?id=134" class="postimage" alt="12916783_803642576447396_2675235107696681148_o.jpg" onclick="viewableArea(this);" /></dt></dl></div><div class="inline-attachment"><dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><img src="https://forum.salafiri.com/download/file.php?id=133" class="postimage" alt="12994396_803642606447393_7568339536383201444_n.jpg" onclick="viewableArea(this);" /></dt></dl></div><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Sat Apr 01, 2017 2:23 pm</p><hr />
