<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=1420&amp;p=1516#p1516"><![CDATA[
<strong><span style="color: #FF0000">READINGS IN AMAL QURANI OF MAULANA ASHRAF ALI THANWI<br /><br />PART 10</span></strong><br /><br />Okay, so this one is so bad that I had to have it checked in case I was making a mistake. I read it upto 10 times again and again trying to make tawil of it but I could not.<br /><br />This is the reality of Mawlana Ashraf Ali Thanwi and the discredited Deobandi sect. Forget childbirth and it's complication Mawlana Thanwi has taken it to some next level. All I can say the blind followers of Mawlana Thanwi should take account of themselves and their blind insane love for the Deobandi sect. <br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br /><strong><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal"><span style="color: #FF0000">Mawlana Thanwi says<br />TO EASE CHILDBIRTH<br />Write the following ayahs (on paper) and then tie them to left thigh (of the pregnant woman) for an easy childbirth, In Sha Allah the birth will be very easy. However after childbirth the tawiz should be opened immediately and then the smoke of the woman's hair (ie the woman's hair should be cut and then burnt and the smoke generated) should be allowed to rise towards her private parts (ie vaginal area) as this will be beneficial for childbirth. (Amal Qurani pp.33 of Mawlana Ashraf Ali Thanwi and endorsed by Mufti Muhammad's Shafi, Mawlana Taqi Usmanis Father)</span></span></strong><br /></div></blockquote><br /><br /><div class="inline-attachment"><dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><img src="https://forum.salafiri.com/download/file.php?id=132" class="postimage" alt="11218202_786579564820364_4920713128634770405_n.jpg" onclick="viewableArea(this);" /></dt></dl></div><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Sat Apr 01, 2017 2:19 pm</p><hr />
