<span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal"><span style="color: #FF0040"><strong>PART 1</strong></span></span><br /><br />The people of innovation are always attacking our scholars, may Allah have mercy on them.<br /><br />However look at this Maulana Ashraf Ali Thanwi and also Maulana mufti Muhammad Shafi, the father of Maulana Taqi and Rafi Uthmani. He worked on the following book, added the References to the Quran and added other benefits, where is the reprimand for the following action.<br /><br />Let the likes Mohammad Yasir, Usamah Muttakin and their other sympathisers ponder over the following and tell us what their elders believed. This also applies to Abdur rahman ibn Yusuf and others like him who are ardent defenders of Maulana Thanwi.<br /><br /><div class="inline-attachment"><dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><img src="https://forum.salafiri.com/download/file.php?id=120" class="postimage" alt="12715574_769687646509556_100200482467345914_n.jpg" onclick="viewableArea(this);" /></dt></dl></div><br /><div class="inline-attachment"><dl class="file"><dt class="attach-image"><img src="https://forum.salafiri.com/download/file.php?id=121" class="postimage" alt="12705676_769687613176226_8482920356318274099_n.jpg" onclick="viewableArea(this);" /></dt></dl></div><br /><br />Translation<br /><br /><blockquote class="uncited"><div><br /><strong><span style="color: #FF0000"><span style="font-size: 150%; line-height: normal">If the (woman) fails to get pregnant or she fears the pregnancy will not last then write both this ayah and the previous one and tie it to the woman's private part, inshaAllah tala her pregnancy will be preserved and she will remain pregnant if it was not holding. (Amal Qurani pp.24 2nd line from the top) of Maulana Ashraf Ali Thanwi)</span></span></strong><br /></div></blockquote><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=48">AbuKhuzaimahAnsari</a> — Sat Apr 01, 2017 1:48 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
